---

# 🎁 Gift Rush

## Story

Birthday gifts have been scattered across the world.

Players must collect them and deliver them before the party starts.

---

# 👥 Player Limit

Solo

2–10 Players

---

# 🎯 Objective

Collect gifts.

Deliver them to:

🏠 Houses

🤖 Buddy

🎂 Birthday Hall

All three delivery locations provide different rewards.

---

# 🎁 Gift Types

Examples:

🎈 Balloon Gift

🍫 Chocolate Gift

🧸 Toy Gift

🎂 Cake Gift

🎀 Premium Gift

💎 Golden Gift

🌈 Rainbow Gift

🎉 Mystery Gift

Each gift has different rarity.

---

# 🎁 Carry System

Players normally carry

3 Gifts

Players may carry more.

However:

- Movement Speed decreases.
- Jump becomes weaker.
- Carrying too many gifts becomes risky.

---

# 👹 Enemies

Players may encounter Cake Monsters while delivering gifts.

They patrol the map and chase careless players.

---

# 😂 Funny Items

Players can prank each other.

Examples:

🍌 Banana Peel

🎈 Balloon Push

🧊 Ice Trap

💨 Wind Gun

🎁 Fake Gift

🎊 Confetti Bomb

🪣 Paint Bucket

Purely for fun.

---

# 🤝 Teamwork

Players may:

Drop Gifts

Pass Gifts

Throw Gifts

Share Gifts

Work together for faster deliveries.

---

# ⭐ Combo System

Continuous deliveries increase combo.

Examples:

Combo x2

Combo x3

Combo x5

Higher combo gives bonus rewards.

---

# 🏆 MVP Awards

