- Friendship XP
- Anniversary Cosmetics
- Titles
- Badges

---

# Long-Term Vision

Cake Defense and Gift Rush are designed as cooperative Anniversary games focused on teamwork, strategy, social interaction, party fun, and replayability while helping Buddy celebrate the biggest birthday in Roblox Buddy AI.

